This fixture is a small Go module for read-only preview integration
coverage against gopls. The source is intentionally not gofmt-formatted so the
formatting and range-formatting previews return edits without mutating files.

Markers embedded in the source drive the test:

  hover=answer   marks the constant queried by textDocument/hover.
  rename=message marks the function declaration queried by textDocument/rename.
  query=message  marks a function reference that should be renamed too.

-- go.mod --
module readonlypreview

go 1.27

-- main.go --
package main

import "fmt"

const answer = 42 // hover=answer

func message(name string) string { // rename=message
return fmt.Sprintf("hello %s %d",name,answer)
}

func main() {
fmt.Println(message("gopher")) // query=message
}
